description: The husband & wife team of Douglas and Sumalee Somerville have become an important part of Fremont's dinning scene since they opened up Kaosamai Thai Restaurant & Caterers in 2001. This tasty mobile kitchen brings you Phad Thai, PaNang Curry, Cashew Chicken, Spring Rolls, and more on the streets of the Seattle area. If you're in the mood for some tasty Thai, look no further than Kaosamai!
name: Kaosamai Thai
